body:
when use "decorator stage3" with this option that `context.metadata` will be `undefined`

```js
const option = {
    jsc: {
        parser: {
            syntax: 'typescript',
            decorators: true,
        },
        transform: {
            decoratorVersion: '2022-03',
        },
        target: 'es5',
        externalHelpers: true, // external @swc/helpers
    },
    module: {
        type: 'es6',
    }
}
```

if set `externalHelpers` to `false`, `context.metadata` is right

example code 

```ts
function Get() {
  return (value, context) => {
    console.info(context.metadata); // out undefind
  };
}

class MyClass{
    @Get()
    doSome(){
        //..
    }
}
```
